[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     68[0m:[38;5;10m[49m # to CloudWatch Logs Insights for cross-call investigation. The
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     69[0m:[38;5;10m[49m # snapshot, the per-patient features, and the per-patient hazard
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     70[0m:[38;5;10m[49m # scores are PHI. Log structural metadata only (run_id, snapshot_ts,
