[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    592[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     See pseudocode Step 1 in the main recipe. Returns a list of
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    593[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     state records the inflow, outflow, and composition steps
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    594[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     consume. Each record carries enough context for the survival
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    595[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     model to score it without a second HealthLake round trip.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    596[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     """
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    597[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     iso_now = snapshot_ts.isoformat()
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    598[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     active_encounters = healthlake.search_in_progress_encounters(
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    599[0m:[38;5;10m[49m         as_of_ts=iso_now)
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    600[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    601[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     state_records = []
