[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    907[0m:[38;5;10m[49m             hazard = self.hazard_per_hour(features, target_hour)
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    908[0m:[38;5;10m[49m             # Per-hour discharge probability conditional on
